room_title: Escape room "The Quest" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_address: 611 N. Wilcox Street, Castle Rock, CO 80104
room_description: The Middle Realm, a land of beauty and great magical power has existed in harmony for ages. Now, the Middle Realm is under siege by the evil Mortas, who has placed a spell of darkness over the land. The Oracles have summoned you, the heroes, to come to Middle Realm’s aid. You and your team must find and claim the Dragon Sword and vanquish evil from the land. This is the Quest, a hero’s adventure.
